data.description: Welcome to 3538 Turtle Cove! This stunning house is now available and offers a fantastic opportunity to make it your dream home. Situated on a fabulous private lot, this extensively renovated property boasts a spacious and inviting interior.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and bright living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones. The great room features a cozy fireplace and dry bar, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open kitchen, breakfast room, and separate dining room provide ample space for preparing and enjoying meals together. The primary suite is truly a retreat, featuring a vaulted ceiling, custom built-in storage, and two huge walk-in closets. Additionally, there are three nicely sized secondary bedrooms that offer flexibility for your specific needs. This home has been recently updated with new luxury vinyl flooring on the main level, new carpet in the bedrooms, fresh interior and exterior paint, new lighting, hardware, professional landscaping and so much more! Outside, you'll find a large, screened porch and fenced yard surrounded by mature trees, offering privacy and tranquility. Located in a wonderful swim/tennis community, this property also benefits from excellent schools nearby. Plus, you'll have convenient access to dining, shopping, and parks in the area. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home!
